                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Do more -- and have more fun -- than you ever thought possible with Apple's portable jukebox and this easy-to-use guide. Not only will you be able to play music, but you will learn to find, download, and organize your music to get the best sound, use cool accessories, and pick up little-known tips and tricks to enhance your overall iPod experience.</span>
              
</td></tr></table>
