                    <span>I really liked this book. Ita has lots of cool trick and hacks that I hadn't really heard of. Writing was good, but the best part was learning some cool new ways to use my favorite toy. If you want to get them most out of your ipod this is the best book out there.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I picked up info and tips from this book</div>
